<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>V-GUARD AI Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0a192f; color: #ccd6f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; }
        
        /* Dashboard Container */
        .dashboard-container { padding: 40px 20px; }
        
        /* Bagian Profil & Foto */
        .profile-card { 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 30px; 
            background: #112240; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #233554;
        }
        .profile-img { 
            width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; 
            border: 3px solid #64ffda; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        /* Visi & Misi Section */
        .visi-misi-section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
        h2, h3 { color: #64ffda; font-weight: bold; }
        .text-misi { color: #8892b0; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }

        /* Fitur Layanan Cards */
        .feature-card { 
            background: #112240; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; height: 100%; 
            border: 1px solid transparent; transition: 0.3s; text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-card:hover { border-color: #64ffda; transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .feature-card i { font-size: 2rem; color: #64ffda; margin-bottom: 15px; }

        /* Navigasi (Yang Sudah Keluar) */
        .nav-links { margin-top: 50px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; }
        .btn-nav { 
            border: 1px solid #64ffda; color: #64ffda; padding: 10px 25px; 
            text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn-nav:hover { background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container dashboard-container">
    
    <div class="profile-card">
        <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/arinoriashikaga0405-ux/V-GUARD-AI/main/erwin.jpg" alt="Erwin Sinaga" class="profile-img">
        <h1>V-GUARD AI</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary text-uppercase tracking-widest">Cyber Security Solution</p>
    </div>

    <div class="visi-misi-section text-center">
        <h3>Visi & Misi</h3>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="p-3 border-start border-info mb-3">
                    <h5 class="text-info">Visi</h5>
                    <p class="text-misi">Menjadi pionir keamanan digital berbasis AI yang adaptif untuk menjamin kedaulatan data bisnis global.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="p-3 border-start border-info mb-3">
                    <h5 class="text-info">Misi</h5>
                    <p class="text-misi">Memberikan proteksi siber proaktif melalui teknologi deteksi cerdas serta menyederhanakan manajemen keamanan untuk SME melalui dashboard terintegrasi.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
        <h3 class="text-center mb-4">Fitur Layanan Utama</h3>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i>
                <h5>AI Threat Detection</h5>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Deteksi ancaman otomatis 24/7.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                <h5>Automatic Response</h5>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Mitigasi instan serangan siber.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h5>Predictive Analysis</h5>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Analisis celah keamanan sistem.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i>
                <h5>Endpoint Protection</h5>
                <p class="small text-secondary">Proteksi seluruh perangkat jaringan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/portal-klien" class="btn-nav">Portal Klien</a>
        <a href="/admin-dashboard" class="btn-nav">Admin Dashboard</a>
    </div>

</div>

<footer class="text-center py-5 text-secondary">
    <small>&copy; 2026 V-GUARD AI. All Rights Reserved.</small>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
